Andhra Milk  Vale

Fresh from Our Farm to Your Door

Welcome to Andhra delite, a leading milk processing plant dedicated to delivering high-quality dairy products while promoting sustainable farming practices and supporting local communities. With a passion for excellence and a commitment to customer satisfaction, we strive to provide the freshest, safest, and most delicious milk and dairy products.

Our Mission:

To produce exceptional dairy products while prioritizing:

  •  Quality: Uncompromising standards for taste, purity, and nutrition.

  • Sustainability: Environmentally conscious practices and responsible resource management.

  • Community: Empowering local farmers, supporting rural development, and fostering a healthier society.
